<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">śakāptam</hi> Āyirattu Irunūṟṟu toṇṇūṟṟuiraṇṭiṉmel cellāniṉṟa <hi rend="grantha">sā</hi>- <hi rend="grantha">dhāra</hi>ṇa<hi rend="grantha">samvat sara</hi> ttu cittiraimāta mutal
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tiyati nāḷ nāyaṉār tirukkāḷattiuṭaiya nāyaṉār koyiṟ tiruviḷakkuiṭaiyaril varatakkoṉ kāḷatti makaṉ nilakaṇṭa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṉeṉ Eṉ māmaṉ viṭaiykkoṉ Akkappiḷḷai makaṉ kāḷattikku piḷḷai yillātapa<unclear>ṭi</unclear>yāle Ivaṉuṭaiya māṭuāṉatu <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>paṇṭārattile kā<hi rend="grantha">ṭṭi</hi> kkuṭuttu nāyaṉār <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>paṇṭāra Āṉmāṭu nāṉ kaikkoṇṭa cāvā muvā<supplied reason="omitted">p</supplied> pacu Eṭṭu I<hi rend="grantha">ṣabham</hi> Oṉ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṟu<unclear>āka</unclear> Uru 9- ṉāl tiruvi<hi rend="grantha">ḷa</hi> kku va Inta viḷakku kālukku nāḷ Oṉṟukku tirukkāḷattiuṭaiyāṉāl ney<note n="257-1">The record is incomplete.</note>
</p>

